To get started with awesome-config, do the following:

Backup your configuration directory:
cp -a ~/.config/awesome ~/.config/awesome.bak-$(date +%F-%T)

Then copy the example files "rc.lua" and "crappy.json" from
/usr/share/doc/awesome-config-examples to your config directory
"~/.config/awesome".

